    <div class="lineagris"></div>
    <div class="texto14">
        <div style="width:350px;float:left; line-height:22px;">

        Your Swisskip account lets you do one more thing after you die: pass all your online properties to the person you decide. (Let´s call that person your Data-Heir).
        <br /><br />
        Think about it: each day you store more and more information online. All that info (bank accounts,
        insurance accounts, stock accounts, mail accounts, social network accounts...) are in your computer, or at the cloud, or at the web, or in your tablet, or in
        your smartphone... locked behind passwords, out
        of reach of your family, friends, or partners.
        <br /><br />
        And when you are not around anymore... well, that’s when your Swisskip account will come <br /><br />
        Swisskip is a simple and ultra-secure solution that helps you pass your important information to your chosen Data-Heir.<br /><br />

        </div>
