        <span class="rojo18"><strong>“One more thing, honey...”</strong></span><br /><br />

        <div style="width:350px;float:left; line-height:22px;">Choose any one you like for your Data-Heir, your spouse, your husband, your son, your daughter, your closest relative, your best friend, your partner. All we need is a name and a e-mail. Swisskip will take care of the rest.</div>
        <div style="width:350px;float:left; margin-left:20px; line-height:22px;">Your Data-Heir will not have access to any of your data until you are not with us anymore. Once your passing is confirmed, he or she will receive a last letter from you, with the access to your Swisskip account.</div>
