            You can store any thing you want in your Swisskip account: pictures, videos or documents, accounts, passwords... All the info you upload to Swisskip will be encrypted with the latest safety technology and will only be passed to your Data-Heir once your
            death has been confirmed.
            <br /><br />
            For your most sensitive information, such as bank accounts and passwords you might
            like to choose our patented Swisskip Splitter.
